        "TileImage": "$($repository 6d5bf7f7-56bb-4329-acbd-2c6f341f0d79).Image",
        "Description": "Everyone around here is responsible for guarding this building.\rI know it, Christopher May knows it, the boss knows it, we all know it.\rHowever, this Christopher May guy, had the boss buy him his own little personal building to stand around in.\rEveryone one here knows it isn&apos;t fair and we have put together a fundraiser to pay a hitman to take him out, once and for all.\rIn addition to the three dollars you will be awarded, we will give you a paperclip and some bubblegum.\rThanks 47.",
